summary: 5 Norwegians head for a cabin in the wilderness for a few days of team building. But strange things start happening - especially down by the water where they find an abandoned tent. Is there someone else?
cast: Bjørn Floberg|Kristoffer Joner|Eva Röse|Sampda Sharma|Marko Iversen Kanic|Simon Norrthon|Ivar Nørve|Torstein Løning|Cecilie De Lange|Bjørn Jenseg|Sigbjørn Solheim|Andreas Bjorøy
title: Bosque tenebroso
